high_descs: Turn around to face the cabinet below the coffee maker.
Pick up the bowl in the cabinet.
Turn right and step forward to face the fridge.
Cool the bowl in the fridge and remove it.
Look up the face the cabinet on the right above the fridge.
Place the bowl in the cabinet above the fridge.
anns.task_desc: To cool a bowl plus place it in the right cabinet above the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the cabinet with the Keurig on it.
Take the brown bowl out of the cabinet under the Keurig.
Turn to your right and walk to the refrigerator on the left.
Put the bowl in the refrigerator, leave it until it gets cold, then take it out.
Put the bowl in the cabinet over the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold bowl in the cabinet over the refrigerator.

high_descs: Turn around to the cupboard under the coffee maker
Take out the bowl from the cupboard
Go right and walk around the island counter to the refrigerator on the left
Open the refrigerator door and place the bowl to the left of the potato and close the door. Open the door and take the bowl out of the refrigerator
Turn left in a full circle and look to the cupboard above the refrigerator
Put the bowl in the cupboard to the left of the salt
anns.task_desc: Put a cooled bowl in a cupboard
